Ok, let us summarize. Your immune system has&nbsp;
two parts, one that defends you right after&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:13.680 --> 00:09:17.760
birth and one that carries the largest&nbsp;
library of superweapons in the universe&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:17.760 --> 00:09:23.440
but needs to boot up first. To create billions&nbsp;
of different superweapons, your adaptive immune&nbsp;&nbsp;

